{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"186a9e17aa84a7d2d2685ce23cb1bd9530d27da219dbc1b92767f54189302364","slug":"management-office","location":"/roadmap/org/management_office.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"建设管理办公会制度","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/roadmap/org/management_office.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/roadmap/org/management_office.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"management_office.md","url":"/management_office-b546174869f1634fdea8bb591d8013a3.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公司近期主要工作重点之一是建设公司的管理办公室制度，以提高对于 KA 和 LA 客户的服务能力。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"EMgthLWKgi"}],"key":"gVKGnOfdtZ"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"什么是管理办公室？","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"QMq5jFuMmP"}],"identifier":"id","label":"什么是管理办公室？","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"zLgm4jGUKK"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"管理办公室是具备管理职能的部门。由于量潮实行分布式日常运营管理的基本组织思路，因此在公司代表大会及其下属专业委员会闭会期间，公司的各个管理办公室会负责某一块的管理工作。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"DTLimQtmja"}],"key":"CzwvjsnqxP"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前公司的管理办公室包括 CEO 办公室、COO 办公室、CTO 办公室、量潮数据办公室（简称 BU 办公室）、财务部、人力资源部六个管理办公室。实际上所有的部门未来都会分摊一部分管理职责，比如商务部也正在向管理办公室转型。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"wEOARh4bTl"}],"key":"m4mPIW0mXx"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据 BU 办公室主要负责指导下属的业务部门响应客户、集中处理疑难问题和复盘。人力资源部和财务部分别负责本职能决策。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"nRkZJIca6j"}],"key":"IjFwUUeaDc"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CEO 办公室主要负责战略决策和平台研发，COO 办公室和 CTO 办公室主要负责业务的管理和技术。同时三个办公室还分工兼任课堂业务的管理职责。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"XmDBqCtsbM"}],"key":"C55ZcfGz0H"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每个管理办公室维持两三人的规模，基本配置是一个主管和一个秘书。不同的管理办公室会根据实际人员情况在上述框架下调整。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"YTPsf3I1Hs"}],"key":"koUQ8zC11y"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"秘书处下属的 CEO 办公室、COO 办公室和 CTO 办公室已经经过比较系统的培训，接下来是要培训秘书处以外的各个管理办公室，帮助他们建立部门工作章程。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"fH5hcnq7oT"}],"key":"sgIxos8ZhO"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么要建立管理办公室制度？","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"STUhU5s1BV"}],"identifier":"id","label":"为什么要建立管理办公室制度？","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"asnBLwmDng"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这是我们基本的组织契约“向下放权、向上揽责”的直接体现之一。通过公司代表大会及其专业委员会下放“行政权”给管理办公室，以确保公司内外部的各项日常事务可以及时响应。","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"UgQOD31wNS"}],"key":"VNP57dg5Ne"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"随着公司业务规模和范围的不断增长和复杂化，我们逐渐意识到分布式管理的重要性。只有批量培养领导者并围绕领导者们建立管理小组，才能够应对越来越复杂的业务协同。","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"CV7Cvl99lt"}],"key":"Cz6MfwMsL1"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这和我们的项目制服务模式也有很大的关系。项目制服务相比于产品制服务，决策密度更大、决策更为分散，因此也更不适合集中决策。","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"mSkay6B3KU"}],"key":"UMopuwMYt0"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前来看，主要的问题是转型管理办公室的过程中缺乏系统的培训和制度改革，导致管理办公室在不断下放权责给一线以后找不到自身定位，而在系统预设的框架中本该管理办公室承担的职责没有人履行。","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"tRbYCHTZT6"}],"key":"i1aDqXZ7oJ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在最近的突击检查中，我已经注意到一些长线服务出现中断的情况。团队缺乏有效的记忆和建档协同习惯，以及缺乏定期回顾的习惯，又经常容易被加队的客户和事务打断注意力。我们已经注意到几个项目的进度异常，并且正在排查其中的原因和改进。","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"dV9WnAddqc"}],"key":"rcKtWojHhB"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对客户的承诺","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"IjQcVGpovG"}],"identifier":"id","label":"对客户的承诺","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"O5A1rFa8rC"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建设管理制度是我们自己的责任，积极披露管理制度以提高客户信任度也是我们的责任。","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"OBsSMk2q6r"}],"key":"vW5UBCL3iU"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们会通过工程章程、工作手册等资料明确披露我们对客户承担的权责，方便客户理解和追踪。","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"pJVMB23d7m"}],"key":"QfnAvmSZXp"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们也正在积极研发 AI 原生平台，打通我们与客户、公司内部之间的协作网络。以促进工作记忆在团队内外部的持久化流转。","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"IzKMlUrWPE"}],"key":"YFcP0ulBkz"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们尽我们所能搭建一个可溯源、可审计的系统，为客户提供稳定、高效、可靠的服务。","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"key":"w4jFIt4008"}],"key":"ACbZm5uDWc"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"办公室管理制度改进建议（2026年3月反馈）","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"key":"DaoLfp8Kzj"}],"identifier":"id-2026-3","label":"办公室管理制度改进建议（2026年3月反馈）","html_id":"id-2026-3","implicit":true,"key":"Ym5gMyoQPH"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一、紧急程度评估","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"key":"e8V3h1u0AK"}],"identifier":"id","label":"一、紧急程度评估","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"YKC3fh4ZD6"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"- 紧急程度评估（Triage）： 办公室需建立三级响应机制。","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"key":"INeO96J0iK"}],"key":"kkgt1IzUMd"}],"key":"Hb2R1K6AhG"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":49,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"L1（内部流转）： 日常进度、小修小改，由办公室自行决策，但必须**“工作留痕”**。","position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"key":"mbA12I2PbJ"}],"key":"xkmnLwD0jd"}],"key":"yOQfQg25vt"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"L2（协调介入）： 跨部门卡顿、资源短缺，由办公室发起协调请求。","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"key":"HaskxU3FnV"}],"key":"TupKS9RB7s"}],"key":"oPSCOTi6Qe"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":47,"column":1},"end":{"line":49,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"L3（秘书处介入）： 涉及重大经营风险、现金流项目，由秘书处定夺。\n","position":{"start":{"line":47,"column":1},"end":{"line":47,"column":1}},"key":"AaRVFr8IXP"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":47,"column":1},"end":{"line":47,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"- 风险消除复盘： 以某个项目为案例，复盘卡顿点。以后凡是涉及“多次交付”的项目，必须实施事前/事中/事后三阶段管理。","position":{"start":{"line":47,"column":1},"end":{"line":47,"column":1}},"key":"uNuphcvIui"}],"key":"g2AlK4JbaW"}],"key":"dI1XOBHWdi"}],"key":"FlflcLUhej"}],"key":"mcbSNKC4W5"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"二、 强化“以结果为导向”的硬性考核","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"key":"inrBMkQB4o"}],"identifier":"id","label":"二、 强化“以结果为导向”的硬性考核","html_id":"id-4","implicit":true,"key":"INDgZF7zaZ"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":54,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"零信任校验： 验收项目不仅听口头汇报，必须看交付物、校验工时。","position":{"start":{"line":51,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"key":"qZ5wHg84oF"}],"key":"ieHfaXHXqi"}],"key":"QDvr1TWmVm"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1},"end":{"line":52,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"节点强约束： 在项目策划书阶段锁定 DDL。未按时完成且未提前预警的，直接挂钩绩效惩处。","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1},"end":{"line":52,"column":1}},"key":"Je9ZgnW78b"}],"key":"qid3LBuTRN"}],"key":"jbNSGCVXen"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":54,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"项目经理穿透： 要求 PM 能够直接接触代码/底层数据，防止一线人员因信息差导致的瞒报。","position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"key":"hPyAGG5o9z"}],"key":"SdrCHUUfkq"}],"key":"U6xDszoODT"}],"key":"AH7Z3pmaR8"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":55,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"三、 数字化工作日志与建档","position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":55,"column":1}},"key":"Ega512N3J5"}],"identifier":"id","label":"三、 数字化工作日志与建档","html_id":"id-5","implicit":true,"key":"FZP9xLZBuk"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":1},"end":{"line":56,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"同步追踪： 强制执行项目日志，重点记录“客户需求变更”。","position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":1},"end":{"line":56,"column":1}},"key":"mmFtg4fajj"}],"key":"W2SKGYoDnA"}],"key":"lEuaiMpAU7"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":57,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"现金流优先级： 在协同工具中高亮标注“直接进账项目”，此类项目拥有最高的资源调用权重。","position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":57,"column":1}},"key":"VsH6STcmli"}],"key":"wLH9qX4iqH"}],"key":"UgTRUUiHKQ"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":58,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"主动询问制： 明确秘书/办公室人员不仅仅是传声筒，必须在关键节点主动向负责人索要进度，而非等待汇报。","position":{"start":{"line":58,"column":1},"end":{"line":58,"column":1}},"key":"rUZ2aXBcx6"}],"key":"zgZGAerRTJ"}],"key":"hLM2P9lFBu"}],"key":"O1CWlipUL5"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":60,"column":1},"end":{"line":60,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"四、 商业补救与激励机制","position":{"start":{"line":60,"column":1},"end":{"line":60,"column":1}},"key":"E3ss44UAZu"}],"identifier":"id","label":"四、 商业补救与激励机制","html_id":"id-6","implicit":true,"key":"oEoibAwvIl"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":62,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"商务补偿标准： 研究制定“项目延误/质量瑕疵”的补偿方案（优惠券、退款等），倒逼管理层重视交付质量。","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"key":"TCdZhUVs8N"}],"key":"sbWWeuOayp"}],"key":"mmq4KpgcIj"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":62,"column":1},"end":{"line":62,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"预设不符预警： 针对“接手后发现与预设不符”的情况（有同事提到），建立 24 小时上报机制，若在规定时间内未反馈异议，则视为默认预设可行。","position":{"start":{"line":62,"column":1},"end":{"line":62,"column":1}},"key":"LP7z8RrAia"}],"key":"IQvOaol4cQ"}],"key":"LHGMWVjXIi"}],"key":"eWrehjNTc2"}],"key":"DGx8lV1HX4"}],"key":"dFcUS5MQHs"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}